武汉“方舱三姐妹”，都出院了。
Wuhan "three sisters square cabin," were discharged from hospital.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 吴怡 通讯员 张阳 刘文琴3月4日下午，在武汉华中科技大学附属协和医院西院区7楼东区，5名新冠肺炎患者集中出院。
Wu Yi Correspondent Zhang Yang Liuwenqin March 4 afternoon, Wuhan Huazhong University of Science and Technology affiliated Concorde Hospital West District 7 East, five patients were discharged from the hospital.
澎湃新闻从中山大学孙逸仙纪念医院了解到，该医院第二批支援湖北疫情防控医疗队自2月8日接管重症病区7楼东区以来，已累计治愈出院15人，另有部分患者病情转轻后转院。
The hospital's second batch of support for the Hubei Outbreak Prevention and Control Team has cured 15 people since it took over the seventh floor of Eastern District on February 8, according to the Sun Yat-sen Memorial Hospital of Zhongshan University.
医疗队领队、医院党委副书记兼副院长许可慰教授介绍，此次出院的5位患者年龄最大的66岁，最小的33岁。
Medical team leader, hospital deputy secretary and vice-president Li Mu said the five patients discharged from the hospital were 66 years old and 33 years old.
经过抗病毒、中成药和支持治疗后，体温恢复正常3天以上，呼吸道症状明显好转，肺部CT显示炎症明显吸收，连续两次呼吸道病原核酸检测阴性，达到治愈出院标准。
After antiviral, Chinese patent medicine and supportive treatment, the body temperature returned to normal for more than 3 days, respiratory symptoms significantly improved, pulmonary CT showed significant absorption of inflammation, two consecutive negative RNA tests, and met the criteria for curing discharge.
据了解，3月4日出院的5位痊愈患者中，有3位被医护人员称为“方舱三姐妹”。
It is understood that March 4 discharged from the hospital, three of the five patients were referred to by the medical staff as the "three sisters square cabin."
当时7楼东区是为了缓解重症床位不足而紧急新开的重症病区，“方舱三姐妹”由于病情过重，在2月9日凌晨从江汉方舱医院紧急转入，之后就住在同一间病房的81、82、83床。
At that time, the eastern section of the 7th floor was a newly opened intensive care area to alleviate the shortage of seriously ill beds. Due to their serious illness, the three cabin sisters were transferred urgently from the Jiang Han Square Hospital in the early hours of February 9, and then stayed in the same ward for 81, 82 and 83 beds.
出院之际，“方舱三姐妹”与医护人员合影。
On discharge from hospital, the "three sisters square cabin" and the medical staff photo.
本文均为中山大学孙逸仙纪念医院 供图在方舱医院的时候，“三姐妹”的情况差不多，都是高烧不退，血氧饱和度也一度掉到85%。
This article is the Sun Yat-sen Memorial Hospital of Zhongshan University in the cabin hospital, the "three sisters" situation is the same, are high fever, blood oxygen saturation also once fell to 85%.
“血氧饱和度到了85%就可能会出现呼吸衰竭了，情况是比较危险的。
"When blood oxygen saturation reaches 85 percent, respiratory failure is possible and the situation is more dangerous.
进入病房后我们第一时间进行了氧疗、抗病毒、改善营养、中西医结合治疗等综合治疗方案，三个人的血氧饱和度都很快到了95%以上，治疗效果很好。
When we entered the ward, we had a combination of oxygen therapy, antiviral treatment, improved nutrition, and combined Chinese and Western medicine.
”病区主任周明根介绍，经过十几天的综合治疗，三人相继停止吸氧，体温逐渐恢复正常，最终达到了出院标准。
"Zhou Minggen, director of the department, said after 10 days of comprehensive treatment, the three stopped taking oxygen and their body temperature gradually returned to normal.
出院之际，“三姐妹”在病区护士们自制的心愿墙上写下留言，为医疗队和其他病友加油。
As they were leaving the hospital, the sisters wrote notes on the wall of the nurses' homemade wishes to cheer up the medical team and other sick people.
“云开雾散，脱下口罩的明天不会远，加油”“我们都是英雄”“早点回家跟家人团圆”……病区自制心愿墙上的留言本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
"Cloud scattered, take off the mask tomorrow will not be far, Come on" "We are all heroes" "Home early and family reunion".
